{
  "stem": "22892.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "-- Constantly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was watching the film.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, the film was better than I originally thought.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I though it was-- should I-- OK, you got things going?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Randy dropped off the video and I shoved it in my VCR.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I see my picture, and then--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name-- full name would be Iceek Miller, or Ichock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It comes from the Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--miller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ichock, you asked me it very quickly, because I never spelled my name, Ichock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- it's I-C-H-O-C-K, Ichock, but they called me Iceek, would be I-C-E-E-K.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Miller, M-I-L-L-E-R.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except the Irvin, I was named by my cousins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted my middle name, which would be Jacob.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, we have too many Jacobs in our family, so Irwin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't even pronounce it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It started with Irwin, and then, finally it became Irvin, because I couldn't pronounce the W.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I'm Irvin or Irv from then on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Targowica, Poland, just a small townlet in eastern Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Targowica was spelled T-A-R-G-O-W-I-C-A.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- if you translate it, it's like 'commercial point,' what it meant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an interesting little town with hills and two rivers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born July 12, 1929.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Edel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother's name was Chana.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's maiden name was Pressman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The town-- from my dad used to talk about it and my mom, constantly the wars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even before World War I, there was always battles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's kind of a strategic area, because of the hills and the rivers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that's all I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never was certain how many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would guess about [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] probably 300 families, Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That would be an educated guess.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some Poles and there was some Ukrainians, but mostly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
